Competitors stand in a circle of six  and hold the Tasers to the hands, heads and necks of their fellow participants.

They then twist the barrel, which holds a single cartridge, and pull the trigger to produce an electric shock.

If a competitor winces then they are theatrically dead and out of the game.

The Tasers that feature in the video are made from pneumatic gas pistols with real electro revolvers.

