Michael Pashkov, another participant featured in the video, says: ‘I wanted to get an adrenaline rush and test myself.

‘I have never taken part in such games but I do extreme power [work outs] so I would like to get extreme here too.

‘I suppose that this game is very extreme and checks your male characteristics, staying power and of course your luck.’

